pcb-rnd 2.1.2
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Feature highlight:

1. CAM jobs from the command line with -x and from the GUI with the
   cam export dialog using {f c}

2. live scripting: dialog box with an script editor for real time
   development and experimentation with scripting

4. almost complete KiCad load support for files generated with version 4
   or older

5. optional gerber drill files

6. option to directly export in the excellon format, without any gerber

7. full netlist code rewrite: support for network mapping, renaming, merging

8 actions and GUI for starting a board without a netlist and build
   the netlist from within pcb-rnd

9 new netlist dialog with enchanced functionality (same code for all HIDs)

10. new log window with enchanced functionality (same code for all HIDs);
    log is persistent (messages before GUI startup are not lost);
    export log to file button/action

